  "texts": [
    "The articles on the topic of dynamic pricing in e-commerce have been categorized into various research areas.",
    "Specifically, business economics and computer science are identified as research areas for approximately 45% and 44% of the analysed articles, respectively.",
    "It stands to be mentioned that an article might belong to multiple research areas simultaneously.",
    "The research area of operations research management science covers 28% of the articles, while engineering accounts for 23% of the sample.",
    "It is worth noting that only a small fraction, around 5%, of the articles fall within the domain of mathematics research."
  ]
}